      <details>
        <summary>What is exclusive community content in video marketing?</summary>
        <p>It's video made specifically for a brand's most loyal customers — such as product previews, behind-the-scenes footage, or leader Q&As — that isn't available to the general public.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What are the main benefits of exclusive video content for customer communities?</summary>
        <p>It increases customer satisfaction, encourages user-generated content, and builds a sense of belonging that strengthens long-term loyalty.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What types of community-focused videos work best?</summary>
        <p>Exclusive product previews, behind-the-scenes content, and customer-only Q&A sessions with company leaders are especially effective at deepening engagement.</p>
      </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

